rooms.Name: A Shining Green Portal
rooms.Description:
You have entered a glistening green portal. All around you see distorted
shapes of the place you were, and the place you are now going. Trees and
rocks form and dissolve around you making you feel nauseous. You begin
to drop to your knees to keep from falling into the unknown.

rooms.Name: A Strange New Forest
rooms.Description:
You do not recognize this area. It is lushly grown with firs, pine, and
oak. It is quite beautiful, but has a strange air about it. You wonder
where to go from here.

Exits.Description: Looks like a clearing... What a relief...

You see the portal from which you just came. You are not sure whether you
want that sensation again.

rooms.Name: In the Green Reaches
rooms.Description:
You are wandering through this forest with no sense of direction or purpose.
The trees all around dwarf you, and you are unable to get a bearing on
which way you are facing.

Exits.Description: Looks like a clearing... What a relief...

rooms.Name: The Edge of the Green Reaches
rooms.Description:
You have worked your way to a clearing in the forest. In the distance
you can see mountain spires towering above the land. Dark clouds hover
above the spires as if there as a curse upon them. It doesn't seem like
a very pleasant place to take a stroll.

Exits.Description: Looks like a clearing... What a relief...

rooms.Name: A Dimly Lit Cavern
rooms.Description:
This cavern is oft-used by something. In the corner you see a matted pile
of fur. Scattered about the room are bones of animals, some long since
dead and others recently unlucky. Strange sounds eminate from the darkness.
In the corner of your eye you see something stir...

Exits.Description: A small crevice in the cieling

rooms.Name: Travelling in the Grey Range
rooms.Description:
You are travelling in high mountains. Large rocks hamper your ease of travel.
Dark clouds are rushing into the area with the smell of rain. You should
think about finding shelter soon. It is getting very cold.

ExtraDescs.Description: A thunderhead is forming nearby, looks like nasty weather ahead.

rooms.Name: A Mountain Pass
rooms.Description:
A small pass allows you to enter the mountains. The wind whips quickly
through the pass in the stone cut in the face of the mountain. You aren't
sure if this is where you want to be... You are entering the Grey Range.

rooms.Name: An Arial Cavern
rooms.Description:
After your long and strenuous climb, you feel relieved to see that you have
found a safe place to rest. This cave is fairly well lit and you see no 
sign of inhabitants. Other than a couple of melted suits of chainmail, it
looks pretty deserted. .....chainmail?..... .....MELTED?.....

Exits.Description: It's a long climb down... Watch for falling rocks...

Dark clouds are rushing into the area with the smell of rain. You should
think about finding shelter soon. It is getting very cold.

Exits.Description:
It's a long way down to that lake. You don't believe you can keep a foothold
while climbing down, and falling would really hurt....

ExtraDescs.Description: A thunderhead is forming nearby, looks like nasty weather ahead.

rooms.Name: A Steep Hill to a Lake Filled Valley
rooms.Description:
Do you always do things without looking? Or do you do things against your
better judgement? That REALLY HURT you, I'll bet. If you're still alive
you may be able to appreciate the beauty of this lake. That is, if you
aren't screaming in agony. The water is glistening in the sun...
Sun? That's strange, everywhere else in the mountains is cloudy.
There is a large dark spot underneath the water. This is getting wierd.

Exits.Description: That's the best way to try to climb out of this basin.

rooms.Name: Travelling in the Grey Range
rooms.Description:
The clouds seem to be getting darker. You begin to feel rain on your face.
This dead end doesn't seem too appealing, either. To the north, you hear
hoofsteps.

Exits.Description: A brushpile... Is that a trail?

ExtraDescs.Description:
You see a large amount of brush, you could possibly drag it out of the
way if you really needed to...

think about finding shelter soon. It is getting very cold.

ExtraDescs.Description: A thunderhead is forming nearby, looks like nasty weather ahead.

rooms.Name: A Cross in the Path
rooms.Description:
You run upon a split in the path here. There is a sign posted in the ground.
A path leads off to the north where you can see a vale, or meadow, and
what seems to be a town. The path also continues east, circling the
valley lake where the skies are darkening over the mountains.

Exits.Description: Haven't you figured out that it's a DT yet?

ExtraDescs.Description:
The sign reads:

                    "Durrany's Vale is to the north
                     and will makes a quaint respite
                     from these weary mountains. To 
                     east, few return.
                              
                        -Marcus, Merchant of Wonders"

rooms.Name: Travelling in the Grey Range
rooms.Description:
You are travelling in high mountains. Large rocks hamper your ease of travel.
Dark clouds are rushing into the area with the smell of rain. You should
think about finding shelter soon. It is getting very cold.

Exits.Description: IT'S A DAMN D.T.!!! DON'T GO THERE!!!

ExtraDescs.Description: A thunderhead is forming nearby, looks like nasty weather ahead.

rooms.Name: A Mountain Peak
rooms.Description:
You stand upon one of the highest peaks in Midkemia. To the west you see
the mountains and a small village. To the northeast you see a large city.
Due north you see a vast plain and rising above it, another peak, higher
than the one you stand upon.

ExtraDescs.Description: That is the great city of Krondor. Almost an empire in itself.
It is the plagued village of Shamata.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Mountains
rooms.Description:
Ahh, now you know why there is a road here. Traders such as the ones you see
travel this area constantly, making a living for thier families, and
taking necessary items to those who will purchase them.

Exits.Description: A brushpile... Is that a trail?

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Mountains
rooms.Description:
Dorgin was a nice enough town, but you grow tired of the clouds and
wind. You wish you were back home where you could take a nice long
nap in front of a cozy fireplace. maybe there is a nice inn in
Ravensburg where you could share a story with a stranger?

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Mountains
rooms.Description:
Finally, you are coming to the last hill that will take you into the valley.
This is quite a relief, you think. You are looking forward to that nap.
You feel a warm breeze coming up the hill from the valley below.

rooms.Name: A Path Down the Mountain
rooms.Description:
FINALLY! You are leaving the mountains. Down the hill you run to the plain
below. It's actually getting warm! The road looks more travelled here, you
must be getting close to something...

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Mountains
rooms.Description:
On your way down this slope, you notice a tall peak above you. There seems
to be a small path following a ledge that could take you up there. It
is covered in rockfall and may be difficult to navigate. It looks like
you could see where you're going from there.

Exits.Description: A large amount of rockfall blocks your movement up the ledge.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Mountains
rooms.Description:
You are glad to see that there is no one here to bother you as you
travel on your way out of the mountains. The skies look brighter to the
northeast, and you smile, for that is where you are heading.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Grey Ranges
rooms.Description:
This road will lead you out of the Grey Range. It Takes you to a
nearby Barony called Darkmoor. The closest town is called Ravensburg.
This is the largest road from here to the north, and still is not
safe from thieves and murderers. Take care on your journey, so that
it won't be your last.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Grey Range
rooms.Description:
These mountains were named the Grey Ranges due to the ever present
storm clouds that forever loom overhead. Soon you will be out of these
dreary maountains and in the sweet smelling valley of Darkmoor.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Mountains
rooms.Description:
As you walk you begin to think that there should be no one to bother
you on your journey to Darkmoor. People just over-react. You begin to head
down a hill and off of the mountains.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: A Three-Way Crossroad
rooms.Description:
You have come to a Tee in the road. The east and south look more travelled
than does the west, but take your pick...

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: Another Dead End
rooms.Description:
Well, this didn't go anywhere... Looks like an old logging road. Is that 
something rattling around in the bushes?

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
You have travelled a long journey. You hope that rest comes soon. It is 
beautiful out here, though. The road seems to be heavily travelled here.
There is a sign next to the road.

rooms.Name: Another Fork in the Road
rooms.Description:
Looks like a marketplace to the northwest... But the road is more travelled
to the northeast.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: The Crossroads Marketplace
rooms.Description:
You are at the Crossroads Marketplace... Here you'll find food, drink, and
possibly some fun.

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: Entering Ravensburg
rooms.Description:
You are almost in the town of Ravensburg, in the Barony of Darkmoor. The 
town lies to the east. To the north, you see a small apple orchard. It
lies on the other side of a white picket fence.

rooms.Name: The King's Highway
rooms.Description:
You are now on the largest road yet. Many wagons and teams of horses
have travelled this stretch. You see sign here.

rooms.Name: The King's Highway
rooms.Description:
All around you see a beautiful grassy plain, with trees growing heavier
to the west. This road is quite easily travelled, and you see quite a few
people doing just that... travelling.

rooms.Name: The King's Highway
rooms.Description:
The trees get pretty dense in this section of the plains. it seems you
will run into forest before too long. You see a mountain range to the
northwest and the sky is beautiful and clear.

rooms.Name: The King's Highway
rooms.Description:
You have left the plains now and have entered a forest. The road is
well travelled and you feel pretty safe, for guard occasionally pass
you.

rooms.Name: The King's Highway
rooms.Description:
A huge tower of rock climbs up to the north. It is an impressive piece of
nature. It must be three hundred feet high! Only the most brave could
climb that spire!

rooms.Name: The King's Highway
rooms.Description:
As you look to the north you see a mountain range, and around you is a 
beautiful forest. Guards occasionally pass you, and pay you no heed.

rooms.Name: The King's Highway
rooms.Description:
As you continue, you begin the smell a salty breeze from the west.
You realize that you must be getting close to Krondor and the Bitter Sea.

rooms.Name: Entering Krondor
rooms.Description:
The great city of Krondor lies before you. The river drifts lazily into
the city from the north. You can tell that this is a place of great
importance, power, and influence in this world. This is an empire for
you to conquer....or perhaps save....

rooms.Name: Entering Krondor
rooms.Description:
Krondor lies before you. A great city to visit. Lots of people to see, 
talk to, or destroy. An empire for you to conquer....or perhaps save....

rooms.Name: A Road Through the Plain
rooms.Description:
A beautiful grassy plain... The clouds are leaving... The birds are singing..
The sun is shining... The thieves have taken your money... Yes, it IS a 
beautiful day... For someone with your money...

rooms.Name: A Turn in the Road
rooms.Description:
There is a sharp bend in the road here. The path seems much less worn as
it continues west. You notice a small trail, possibly made by animals,
leading into some brush.

Exits.Description: A small trail leads under the brush...

rooms.Name: A Path Leading Toward the Ocean
rooms.Description:

rooms.Name: A Secluded Beach
rooms.Description:
The white sand reflects the sun so well that it almost blinds you. You
stand in awe of this great body of water as you watch the waves roll
in and out to sea.

rooms.Description:
So, you have found the trail. The training grounds are southwest from here.
Go see what you can find out there.

rooms.Name: The Road Going Up the Mountain
rooms.Description:
GREAT! A big, steep hill to climb! The road twists and winds it's way up
into the mountains. It still looks like it's going to storm up there. You
think this mountain sucks...
